{"type": "article", "id": 15427, "title": "时装周街拍，简洁和经典款球鞋大获全胜", "description": "我们从纽约和伦敦时装周的街拍里精选了一些值得一看的球鞋照片。", "date": "2015-09-24T08:29:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 2914, "name": "跑鞋"}, {"id": 1898, "name": "时装周"}, {"id": 7227, "name": "街拍"}, {"id": 15331, "name": "简洁"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 3727, "name": "锐步"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 230, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607134435qa2KZuAQSsC3kRNi.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t最具街头气质的 Sneaker 们，当然很适合街拍。有人喜欢它的舒适，有人喜欢它的百搭和随性。最近进行的时装周秀场外，也少不了这一潮人必备单品的身影。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134424h5fpdMtE68kGJaNA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.77777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t你会发现，最受欢迎的还是一些简洁、纯色系的百搭款，比如 Stan Smith、Adidas 简单的三道杠、一脚蹬（slip－on）和帆布鞋。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t纯黑和纯白，既可以一身黑或白出现，也可以穿得花枝招展最后用一双极简的球鞋来平衡。像下图黑白无袖上装和阔腿裤，加一双连 logo 都不带的球鞋就很不错。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134425JrEYpRMZ1Na4zXgm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.34143969\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134425XplOFjwWsq0ze8Ct.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t秀场外简直让 Stan Smith 称王称霸，这双后面的绿标和绿裙子、绿包袋作细小的点缀还挺妙：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134426uevtOn829DJogTKU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134427coSy6FrkYUdiqNf8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134427vDIaSx7rRByzpX8V.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.32644628\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tAdidas 家的 Stan Smith 这么火，自己的三道杠标识也不少见，简单的鞋型，牛仔、阔腿裤、黑裙子……随便一套就可以出门：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071344286zKH0CWJ1fYqB9MS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.7303719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t少男少女最爱的帆布鞋，洋溢着青春的气息，不过对腿型没任何修饰作用，腿不够细还是换双复古款跑鞋吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134428OIozKwRT9L5XlQfP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"2.09581498\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t纯黑色的帆布鞋还可以用来装酷，如果你有大长腿的话，效果加倍。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134429sj8uWR7BVrGqteZg.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.32599119\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t当然少不了 Nike 的各种款：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071344290Z6Xrx3mOMAnHQ8v.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"3.34917355\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这两年很流行的一脚蹬：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134430uYjRyFt0m7WMdlhb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:justify;\" data-ratio=\"1.3537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134431ET71Dc4oyLGrpQAX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\">以及下面一些鞋类特写：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134431PTLyc79nz4ei3BgA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tAlexander Wang\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134432weR1UiCs2jLJO0SD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tY－3\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134432ONjs9QGXYbawFd0T.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t有着 Y－3 血统的 <span style=\"text-align:left;\">Adidas Tubular </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134433F70KvzJhufib4Xsp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134434BYjhiVLUfEagXGc5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134434aRur4kGH8Bdij26Y.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}